if you re-use/continue it in any way
please insert my name somwhere.

greetings:
----------
i would like to greet all the guys on the blitzlist, i no longer
subscribe. had a great time with ya ! thanks for all. i'm sorry
to quit now. but my time is squeezing me to death :-/
special greetings go to morten lehmann, who disappeared
mysteriously. maybe he reads it ?

